verses.1: Amauʼ gamtatna ah paubaan om loin Topaʼ ngeina sungah a gamtate thupha ngah ahi hi.
verses.2: Ama thuhilhnate zui-in, a lungsim khempeuh uh tawh amah zongin, khialhna zong bawl loin, ama lampi a zuite, thupha ngah ahi hi.
verses.4: Nangma thuhilhte limtakin zuih dingin thu nong pia hi.
verses.5: Nangma ngeina kipte zuihna ah ka gamtatna kip tahen.
verses.6: Na thupiakte khempeuh mitsuanin nei ka hih manin, kei ka maizum kei ding hi.
verses.7: Nangmah biakna ngeina kipte ka sin khit ciangin lungsim thutang tawh nangmah kong phat ding hi.
verses.8: Nangma ngeina kipte ka zui ding hi; kei hong nusia suak kei in.
verses.9: Tangval khat in ama gamtatna a siangtho mahmah dingin bangci kep ding ahi hiam? Nangma thu zuihna tawh ama gamtatna siangthosak thei ding hi.
verses.10: Ka lungsim khempeuh tawh nang ka hong zong hi. Na thupiaknate panin kei hong pialsak kei in.
verses.11: Nangma tungah kong khialh loh nadingin ka lungsim sungah nangma thu ka khol hi.
verses.12: Topa aw, thupha ngah ta in; na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.13: Nangma hong piak nangmah biakna ngeina kipte khempeuh ka gengen ding hi.
verses.14: Hauhnate khempeuh sangin nangma thuhilhnate nuam ka sa zaw hi.
verses.15: Nangma thuhilhnate lungngaingai-in, nangma lampite ka mitsuan ding hi.
verses.16: Nangma ngeina kipte ah nuam ka sa dinga, nangma thu ka mangngilh ngei kei ding hi.
verses.17: Nungta-in nangma thu ka zuih theih nadingin na nasem pa tungah hong cingh in.
verses.18: Nangma thukham sung panin a lamdang nate ka muh theih nadingin keima mitte hong honsak in.
verses.19: Kei pen hih leitungah peemta ka hi hi; keiʼ kiang panin na thuphate seel kei in.
verses.20: Nangmah biakna ngeina kipte a tawntungin ka lunggulh venvan hi.
verses.21: Nangmah in na thupiaknate panin a pial khia, a kisamsiat, a kiphasakte na thuhilh hi.
verses.22: Na thuhilhnate zui ka hih manin amauʼ hong nuihsatna le hong simmawhnate panin kei hong suaktasak in.
verses.23: Uliante in kei hong langpangin thu a vaihawm uh hangin na nasem pa in na ngeina kipte ngaih sunsun ding hi.
verses.24: Na thuhilhnate ka deih hi. Tuate pen keimah thu hong lakte ahi hi.
verses.25: Guallelin leivui lakah ka lum hi. Na thu om sa bangin kei hong hingsak in.
verses.26: Ka gamtatnate kong gen ciangin nangmah in kei nong dawng hi. Na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.27: Nangma ngeina kipte kei hong theitelsak in. Nangma nasep lamdangte ka ngaih sunsun ding hi.
verses.28: Dahna in kei hong vukcip hi. Nangma thu om sa bangin kei hong tha khauhsak in.
verses.29: A man lo lampite ka zuih khak loh nadingin kei hong kem in. Hong hehpih inla, na ngeinate hong hilh in.
verses.30: Thuman lampi ka teel khin a, na biakna ngeina kipte ka deih hi.
verses.31: Topa aw, na thuhilhnate ka pom hi. Kei hong zahhuaisak kei in.
verses.32: Keima theihna nong zaisak ciangin nangma thupiaknate lawpna tawh ka zui ding hi.
verses.33: Topa aw, na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in. A mong dongin ka zui ding hi.
verses.34: Nangma thute kemin ka lungsim khempeuh tawh ka zuih theih nadingin thu theihtelna hong pia in.
verses.35: Nangma thupiakna lampi ah kei hong paipih in. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua ah nuam ka sa hi.
verses.36: Nangma thuhilhnateʼ lamah ka lungsim awnsak inla, ngah nading bekah awnsak kei in.
verses.37: Bangmahin a kimang lo nate, kei hong kinsak kei inla, nangma thu om sa bangin hong nungtasak in.
verses.38: Na thu hong mangte tungah na thuciamnate, na nasem pa tungah hong kipsak in.
verses.39: Ka kihtak hong kikonate keiʼ kiang pan hei khia in. Bang hang hiam cih leh nangmah biakna ngeina kipte hoih mahmah hi.
verses.40: En in, na thuhilhnate ka lunggulh hi. Na thumanna tawh kei hong hingsak in.
verses.41: Topa aw, na ciamna bangin na itna kip, na hotkhiatna kei tungah hong tungsak in.
verses.42: Tua hileh na thu ka muanna hangin kei hong zahkote ka dawnna ding hong om ding hi.
verses.43: Nangmah biakna ngeina kipte lamenin om ka hih manin a man thu hong gen theisak tawntung in.
verses.44: Nangma thu tatsat loin ka zui ngitnget ding hi.
verses.45: Nangma thuhilhnate zuih ding hanciam ka hih manin nuam takin ka nungta ding hi.
verses.46: Kumpiteʼ mai ah nangma thute ka gen dinga, maizumna ka thuak kei ding hi.
verses.47: Bang hang hiam cih leh ka deih nangma thupiakna zuih ding nuam ka sa hi.
verses.48: Keima deih ahi na thupiakte ka zahtak a, na ngeina kipte ka lung ngaingai ding hi.
verses.49: Keimah nong lametsakna ahi na nasem paʼ tungah na thuciamna hong phawk in.
verses.50: Hih pen ka thuakna ah keima kihehnepna hi a, na thuciamna in kei tungah nuntakna hong pia hi.
verses.51: Mi kiphasakte in kei hong zahko gawp uh a, ahih hangin nangma thupiakna panin kei ka pial kei hi.
verses.52: Topa aw, hun lui lai-a nangmah biakna ngeina kipte ka ngaihsut ciangin ka lung hong nuam hi.
verses.53: Nangma thu a nusia migiloteʼ hangin ka heh a suak hi.
verses.54: Hih leitung ka omna peuh ah nangma ngeina kipte la phuah in ka sa hi.
verses.55: Topa aw, zanin na min ka phawk a, nangma thu ka zui hi.
verses.56: Nangma thuhilhte zui ka hih manin keima tungah hih thupha hong tung hi.
verses.57: Topa pen keima tanh ahi hi. Na thute zuih ding ka kiciam hi.
verses.58: Ka lungsim khempeuh tawh na maipha kong ngen hi. Na thuciamna om sa bangin kei hong hehpih in.
verses.59: Ka gamtatnate ka ngaihsun a, na ngeinate zuih ding ka kiciam hi.
verses.60: Kei kinawhin, na thupiakte zuih ding ka zekai kei hi.
verses.61: Migiloteʼ khau in kei hong vialh hangin nangma thu ka mangngilh tuan kei hi.
verses.62: A thuman na ngeina kipte hangin nangmah a phat dingin zankim laitakin ka tho hi.
verses.63: Kei pen, na thuhilhte a zui, nangmah a hong zahtakte tawh a kikhawl pa ka hi hi.
verses.64: Topa aw, leitung pen nangma itna kip tawh kidim hi. Na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.65: Topa aw, na thuciamna bangin na nasem pa na limbawl hi.
verses.66: Na thupiakte um ka hih manin thu khentel theihna le theih siamna hong hilh in.
verses.67: Gim nong piak ma-in lam ka pial thei zel a, ahih hangin tu-in na thu ka zui hi.
verses.68: Nangmah na hoih a, a hoih nate na sem hi. Na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.69: Mi kiphasakte in keiʼ thu, zuau vive gengen uh a, ahih hangin keimah in ka lungsim khempeuh tawh na thuhilhte ka zui hi.
verses.70: Amauteʼ lungsim in thu theithei loin khikcip a, ahih hangin keimah in nangma thu sung nuam ka sa hi.
verses.71: Nangma ngeina kipte ka sin theih nadingin gimna ka thuak pen kei adingin hoih mahmah hi.
verses.72: Nangma kam sung pan a thu pen kham le ngun tul tampite sangin kei adingin hoih zaw hi.
verses.73: Nangmah in kei hong piangsakin na hong bawl hi. Na thupiaknate ka sin theih nadingin thu theihtelna hong pia in.
verses.74: Nangma thuciamna muang ka hih manin nang hong zahtakte in kei hong mu-in lungdam ding uh hi.
verses.75: Topa aw, nangmah biakna ngeina kipte man hi, ci-in ka thei a, na thumanna hangin kei gim na hong pia hi.
verses.76: Na nasem pa tungah na thuciamna bangin keimah hong hehnem dingin na itna kip a baih sa-in hong omsak in.
verses.77: Ka nuntak theih nadingin kei hong hehpih in. Bang hang hiam cih leh nangma thu nuam ka sa hi.
verses.78: Mi kiphasakte zahhuaisak in. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in khemna tawh kei hong lumlet uh hi. Keʼn ahihleh na thuhilhte ka lung ngaingai ding hi.
verses.79: Na teci pannate a theih nadingun nang hong zahtakte keiʼ lamah hong kiheisak in.
verses.80: Guallelh maizumna ka thuak loh nadingin nangma ngeina kipte a kicing takin a zui zo mi hong hisak ta in.
verses.81: Na hong hotkhiat ding ka ngakngakna-in ka tha bei ta a, nangma thu muangin ka lamen hi.
verses.82: Na thuciamnate ka etetna-in ka mitte tha zaw ta hi. “Cik ciangin hong hehnem ding na hiam?” kong ci hi.
verses.83: Bang hang hiam cih leh kei pen meikhu lak a a kikoih dak savun um tawh ka kibang a, ahi zongin nangma ngeina kipte ka mangngilh tuan kei hi.
verses.84: Na nasem pa in bang tanvei ngak lai ding ka hi hiam? Kei hong bawlsiate cik ciangin thu khen ding na hi hiam?
verses.85: Nangma thu a zui lo, mi kiphasakte in keimah hong siahna-in gum a to uh hi.
verses.86: Nangma thupiakte khempeuh man taktak hi. Amaute in thuman lopi-in kei hong bawlsia uh hi. Kei hong huh in.
verses.87: Amaute in kei hong that zo dektak uh hi. Ahih hangin na thuhilhnate ka mangngilh tuan kei hi.
verses.88: Na kam pan a na teci pannate ka zuih theih nadingin na itna kip tawh kei hong hingsak in.
verses.89: Topa aw, vantungah nangma thu kip tawntung hi.
verses.90: Nangma thumanna khang tawntungin kip hi. Nangmah in leitung na kipsak a, om tawntung hi.
verses.91: Nangma sehna tawh tu dongin amaute kip uh hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh na khempeuh nangma nasem ahi hi.
verses.92: Nangma thu, nuam a sa lo hi leng, ka gim thuakna ah ka kisia khinzo ta ding hi.
verses.93: Nangma thuhilhte ka mangngilh ngei kei ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tuate tawh nong nungtasak hi.
verses.94: Kei pen nangma aʼ ka hi hi. Kei hong hon in. Bang hang hiam cih leh nangma thuhilhte zuih ding ka hanciam hi.
verses.95: Migilote in keimah a hong that dingin hong buk uh hi. Ahih hangin na teci pannate keʼn ka lung ngaingai ding hi.
verses.96: A kicing a a kingaihsun nate khempeuh in mong a neihna ka mu khin a, ahih hangin na thupiakna in mong nei loin zai mahmah hi.
verses.97: Na thu deih mahmah ing. Sun tawntungin ka lungngaihngaih ahi hi.
verses.98: Na thupiakna in ka langte khempeuh sangin a pil zaw-in hong bawl hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh tua pen kei tawh om khawm den hi.
verses.99: Ka siate khempeuh sangin thu ka tel zaw hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh na teci pannate ka ngaih sunsun hi.
verses.100: Khanghamte sangin thu ka tel zaw hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh na thuhilhnate ka zui hi.
verses.101: Na thu ka zuih theih nadingin gamtat sia khempeuh ka pelh hi.
verses.102: Nangmah in hong hilh khin na hih manin na biakna ngeina kipte panin kei ka pial kei hi.
verses.103: Nangma thute khum mahmah a, khuaizu sangin khum zaw hi.
verses.104: Na thuhilhnate hangin thu theihtelna ka ngah hi. Tua ahih ciangin a man lo lampi khempeuh ka mudah hi.
verses.105: Nangma thu pen lam hong lak ding meivak hi a, ka paina lampi ah khuavak ahi hi.
verses.106: A thuman ahi nangmah biakna ngeina kipte a zui dingin ka kiciam khin a, ka kipsak khin hi.
verses.107: Nakpi takin gimna ka thuak hi. Topa aw, nong ciam sa bangin kei hong nungtasak in.
verses.108: Topa aw, phatin kong biaknate hong sang inla, nangmah biakna ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.109: Nisimin ka nuntakna a lauhuai sungah om ngitnget a, ahih hangin nangma thu ka mangngilh tuan kei hi.
verses.110: Migilote in kei thang hong siah uh a, ahih hangin na thuhilhnate panin kei ka pial kei hi.
verses.111: Nangmah biakna ngeina kipte tawntung keima luah ahi hi. Tuate pen keima lungdamna ahi hi.
verses.112: Nangma ngeina kipte ka sih mateng a zui tawntung dingin ka lungsim ka khensat hi.
verses.113: Nangma tungah a thuman lote ka mudah a, ahih hangin keimah in nangma thu ka deih hi.
verses.114: Nang pen keima bukna mun le kei hong hupa na hi hi. Na thuciamna ka muang hi.
verses.115: No, siatna a bawlte aw, Pasianʼ thupiakte ka zuih theih nadingin kei kiang panin paikhia un.
verses.116: Kei ka nuntak theih nadingin na thuciamna tawh kizui-in kei hong huh inla, ka lametna ah kei hong zahhuaisak kei in.
verses.117: Ka suahtak theih nading le na ngeina kipte sungah nuamsa-in ka om ngitnget theih nadingin kei hong huh in.
verses.118: Nangma ngeina kipte panin a pial khiate khempeuh na nil khia hi. Amauʼ khem siamna a mawkna ahi hi.
verses.119: Leitung a migilote khempeuh sik-ek bangin na ngaihsun hi. Tua ahih ciangin na teci pannate ka deih hi.
verses.120: Nang kong zahtakna hangin ka khuasikmul suak a, na thukhennate ka zahtak hi.
verses.121: Thutang thumanin ka gamta hi. Hong nengniamteʼ khut sungah kei hong nusia kei in.
verses.122: Na nasem pa adingin nangmah hong kikham inla, mi kiphasakte hong nengniamsak kei in.
verses.123: Nangma hotkhiatna le a man na thuciamna hong tun ding ka etna-in ka mitte a gim ta hi.
verses.124: Na itna kip tawh kituakin na nasem pa tungah hong bawl inla, na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh in.
verses.125: Kei pen na nasem pa ka hi hi. Na thuhilhnate ka theih nadingin thu theihtelna hong guan in.
verses.126: Topa aw, nangma thu kipalsat khin ahih ciangin thu na khen ding hun hi ta hi.
verses.127: Tua ahih ciangin khamte, le kham hoih pente sangin nangma thupiakna ka deih zaw hi.
verses.128: Tua ahih ciangin na thuhilhnate khempeuh tawh a kituakin kei ka gamta a, a man lo lampi khempeuh ka mudah hi.
verses.129: Na thuhilhnate lamdang pha mahmah a, ka lungsim khempeuh tawh tuate ka zui hi.
verses.130: Na thute gentelna in khua vaksak a, thu thei lote tungah thu theihtelna a guan hi.
verses.131: Na thupiakte ka lunggulhna-in ka kam ka-in ka leii ka kha hi.
verses.132: Nangmah hong itte tungah na hih ngei bangin kei lamah hong kihei-in kei hong hehpih in.
verses.133: Na hong ciam sa bangin ka puk nading panin hong kem inla, keima tungah siatna gualzosak kei in.
verses.134: Nangma thuhilhte ka zuih theih nadingin hong nengniamteʼ kiang pan kei hong hon khia in.
verses.135: Na nasem pa tungah na mai hong taangsak inla, na ngeina kipte hong hilh in.
verses.136: Mite in nangma thu zui lo uh ahih manin ka khitui hawk luanin a luang hi.
verses.137: Topa aw, nang na thuman a, na thukhennate zong thuman mahmah hi.
verses.138: Nangma koih sa ngeina kipte thumanin thutak hi.
verses.139: Ka galte in nangma thu kin het lo uh ahih manin keima hehna mei bangin a kuang hi.
verses.140: Na thuciamnate kician mahmah a, na nasem pa in tuate deih mahmah hi.
verses.141: Kei ka neu a, hong kisimmawh hi. Ahih hangin na thuhilhnate ka mangngilh tuan kei hi.
verses.142: Nangma thumanna kip tawntung a, na thukham zong man tawntung hi.
verses.143: Dahna le lungkhamna ka tungah hong tung a, ahih hangin na thupiaknate nuam ka sakna ahi hi.
verses.144: Na teci pannate a tawntungin thuman hi. Thu theihtelna hong guan in; tua hileh ka nungta ding hi.
verses.145: Ka lungsim khempeuh tawh nang tungah kong kiko hi. Hong dawng in, Topa! Na ngeina kipte ka zui ding hi.
verses.146: Nang tungah kong kiko hi. Na thuhilhnate ka zuih theih nadingin kei hong hon in.
verses.147: Khuavak ma-in tho-in huhna ngenin kong kiko a, nangma thuciamna hong tun ding lamenin ka om niloh hi.
verses.148: Nangma thuciamna a lung ngaingai dingin zan khuavakin ka zan hak hi.
verses.149: Topa aw, na itna kip tawh a kizui-in ka aw hong za inla, nangma thutang tawh kizui-in ka nuntakna hong kem in.
verses.150: Gitloh ngimna tawh kei hong bawlsia mite in kei hong neh ta uh a, amaute in nangma thu ngaihsutin nei lo uh hi.
verses.151: Ahih hangin Topa aw, kei kiangah nang nong nai a, na thupiaknate khempeuh ahi taktak vive ahi hi.
verses.152: Tuate a tawntungin a kip dingin na bawl ahihna thu, nangma thuhilhnate panin sawtpi-in ka thei hi.
verses.153: Ka thuakna hong en inla, kei hong hon khia in. Bang hang hiam cih leh nangma thu ka mangngilh kei hi.
verses.154: Ka thu ah hong pang inla, kei hong suaktasak in. Na ciam sa bangin kei hong hon khia in.
verses.155: Migilote, kihon khia lo ding hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in na thukhamte zui lo uh hi.
verses.156: Topa aw, na hehpihna lian hi. Na biakna ngeina kip tawh a kituakin kei hong hon khia in.
verses.157: Kei hong bawlsiate, ka langte tam mahmah a, ahih hangin nangma thu panin kei ka pial tuan kei hi.
verses.158: Thuman lo mite ka muh ciangin ka kih mahmah hi. Bang hang hiam cih leh amaute in nangma thupiakte zui lo uh hi.
verses.159: Nangma thuhilhnate bangzah takin ka deihna hong ngaihsun in. Topa aw, na itna kip tawh a kizui-in kei hong hon in.
verses.160: Na thubulpi thumanna hi a, a man mahmah, nangmah biakna ngeina kipte khempeuh a tawntungin kip paisuak hi.
verses.161: Uliante in thu om lopi-in kei hong bawlsia uh a, ahih hangin na thute lamdang sa mahmah in ka thupi ngaihsut hi.
verses.162: Van kinusia tampi tak a ngah pa bangin na thuciamna ah ka lung a dam mahmah hi.
verses.163: Zuaunate zadahin ka kih a, ahih hangin nangma thu ka deih mahmah hi.
verses.164: Nangmah biakna ngeina kipte hangin nisimin sagih vei nang kong phat hi.
verses.165: Nangma thu a deihte in lungnopna lianpi ngah uh a, amaute a tuksak zo ding bangmah om lo hi.
verses.166: Topa aw, nong hotkhiat ding ka ngak a, na thupiakte ka sem hi.
verses.167: Na thuhilhnate ka zui a, tuate ka nak deih mahmah hi.
verses.168: Na thuhilhnate le na ngeina kip omte khempeuh hoihtakin ka zui a, ka gamtatna khempeuh nangmah in na hong mu hi.
verses.169: Topa aw, kong kikona aw, na kiang hong tung henla, nangma thu om sa tawh kizui-in thu theihtelna kei hong guan in.
verses.170: Keima thumna in na kiang hong ban henla, nangma thu om sa tawh kizui-in kei hong hon khia in.
verses.171: Na ngeina kipte kei hong hilh na hih manin kong phat tawntung ding hi.
verses.172: Na thupiak khempeuh man mahmah ahih manin nangma thu phatna la ka sa ding hi.
verses.173: Nangma thuhilhte hong zui ka hih manin keimah hong huh dingin a kiging sa-in om tawntung in.
verses.174: Topa aw, nong hotkhiat ding ka lamen a, nangma khut sungah nuam ka sa mahmah hi.
verses.175: Nang kong phat theih nadingin kei hong nungtasak inla, nangmah biakna ngeina kipte kei hong huhsak in.
verses.176: A gammang tuu bangin lam ka pial khin hi. Tua ahih manin na nasem pa hong zong in. Bang hang hiam cih leh nangma thupiaknate ka pelh kei hi.
